AGI - Confirmed the 27-year sentence for Valerio Del Grosso. After two and a half hours of board the first Court of Cassation, at the end of the trial for the murder of Luca Sacchi>, the personal trainer killed in Rome on 24 October 2019 outside of a pub in Appio area. There will be a process of Appello bis for Paolo Pirino, Marcello De Propris and Anastasiya Kylemnyk.&nbsp;
&nbsp;
We are "very satisfied and happy with this third judgment: because Valerio Del Grosso's voluntary murder was recognized against Luca. We are also happy and above all for the appeal of the Attorney General on the involvement of De Propris and Pirino in the contest in Del Grosso. Now we are ready and fighters for this new judgment in appeal." So the AGI lawyer Armida Decina. "I'm satisfied with the judgment even if my son won't give it back." Thus Concetta Galati, mother of Luca Sacchi, leaving the court of Cassation after the sentence. "I hope that Del Grosso will repay his whole punishment, because he does not realize, and perhaps never will, of the pain that he caused by removing a son and a brother to a family," he adds. &nbsp;&nbsp;
